The adjustable shoulder strap provides a hands-free option to the comfortable rolled handles. ReturnPolicy.Description:
We offer a 30-day return policy on the majority of our merchandise. If you are unhappy with your item please contact us for a Return Merchandise Authorization (RMA) number and return the item in the same condition it was received, with original packaging and all tags attached. Buyer is responsible for the cost of return shipping. Original shipping and handling charges will not be refunded. If an item was sold with "Free Shipping," the original, actual outgoing shipping cost will be deducted from the refund amount. All returns are subject to a 20% restocking fee, which will be deducted from the final refund amount. Please use the original shipping box and packing materials when sending your package back to us. We recommend that you insure the package through your carrier of choice and purchase tracking services for your protection. Pack carefully and save the shipping receipt for your records. Only merchandise received by us in original, resaleable condition will be credited. Items marked "Final Sale" are not eligible for returns. 

Due to safety and sanitary reasons, no returns will be accepted on used, opened, or unsealed cosmetic and personal care products. Additionally, no refunds will be given based on the expiration date of a product. (Some of our cosmetic items are rare, limited-edition, or discontinued products that may be past the expiration date and are being sold as is. We will always make it explicitly clear in the description when and if an item is expired, so please read carefully and bid or purchase accordingly.) Cosmetic and personal care products MUST BE SEALED to be eligible for returns. Of course, if an item is grossly misrepresented, we will always work with you to make things right.
